-- BTG Pactual Chile Unit to Request Bank License, La Segunda Says
-- B y   E d u a r d o   T h o m s o n
-- 2012-06-12T20:31:27Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-12/btg-pactual-chile-unit-to-request-bank-license-la-segunda-says.html
Celfin Capital SA, a unit of
 Brazil ’s  Banco BTG Pactual SA (BBTG11) , will present a request to
regulators for a bank license in Chile, Santiago-based newspaper
La Segunda said, citing people with knowledge of the plan that
it didn’t identify.  Celfin and BTG Pactual will offer corporate banking
services and don’t plan to provide retail services, the
newspaper said.  Media relations officers at Celfin didn’t immediately
respond to phone calls requesting comment.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Eduardo Thomson in Santiago at 
 ethomson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Papadopoulos at 
 papadopoulos@bloomberg.net  